-- ║  🌿 NATURAL NO TEXTURE OPTIMIZER                             ║
-- ║  ✅ Removes textures ONLY (keeps original colors!)             ║
-- ║  ✅ Removes VFX (particles, trails, beams)                   ║
-- ║  ✅ Does NOT force gray color                                ║
